---
title: Speedy Honey-Garlic Beef Stir-Fry with Green Onion Rice
description: In this fast stir-fry, ground beef is smothered in a sweet and savoury honey-garlic sauce and paired with sweet bell peppers and tender-crisp zucchini. It's a meal that's both speedy and scrumptious!
